-- Berkowitz Says ‘It Doesn’t Get Any Better’ Than BofA for Value
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2012-02-08T14:17:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-08/berkowitz-says-it-doesn-t-get-any-better-than-bofa-for-value.html
Bruce Berkowitz , investment chief at
Fairholme Capital Management LLC, affirmed his confidence in
 Bank of America Corp. (BAC) , saying  “it doesn’t get any better when
it comes to value investing.”  Berkowitz made the remarks on Charlotte, North Carolina-
based Bank of America in a video posted today on Fairholme’s
website in which he discussed his funds’ holdings.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
 nbuhayar@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  